        <p class="hht-sp-price__sub">For five guests · +$60 each additional guest</p>
        <ul class="hht-sp-price__list">
          <li>Five customized airbrush tans included</li>
          <li>Studio experience for your group</li>
          <li>Complimentary bubbles or mimosas (21+ with valid ID)</li>
